8. Custom Bridge Plugin
File: nancy-memorial-gallery-bridge.zip (ready to install)

Purpose: Bridges WPForms gallery form submissions to 10Web Photo Gallery with one-click moderation. Eliminates manual transfer of submitted photos/videos to the gallery.

What it does:

Captures WPForms submissions automatically
Stores as pending in custom database table (wp_nmb_pending)
Emails admin on each new submission
Shows Gallery Submissions menu in WordPress dashboard
Thumbnail previews of submitted photos; video labels for video files
One-click Approve: copies files to 10Web directory, generates thumbnails, inserts db records with contributor attribution
One-click Reject: moves to rejected tab
Handles multiple files per submission
Handles images and video

Setup after install:

Gallery Submissions → Settings
Enter: WPForms Form ID, 10Web Gallery ID, four field IDs (contributor name, relationship, caption, file upload)
Enable "Allow multiple files" on the WPForms file upload field


